alerts.description: Sheep graziers are warned that cold temperatures, showers and northwesterly winds are expected during Monday and Tuesday. Areas likely to be affected include parts of the North East, Central, West and South Gippsland and East Gippsland forecast districts. There is a risk of losses of lambs and sheep exposed to these conditions.
